<div class="playlist_box"><b>Another option</b></div><P>

The <a href="http://www.blc.org">Boston Library Consortium</a> and the
<a href="http://libraries.mit.edu">MIT Libraries</a> are running a
one-year project with Naxos, a classical music label. Through July
2005, up to 100 individuals at Boston-area schools can access a large
library of Naxos' classical recordings over the Internet on a Windows
or Macintosh computer.<P>

