<p>

LAMP was a joint project of the <a
href="http://www.mit.edu/sipb/sipb.html">MIT Student Information
Processing Board</a> (Josh Mandel/Quentin Smith/Keith Winstein) and <a
href="http://web.mit.edu/mitcable">MIT Cable Television</a> (Randy
Winchester/Jon Ward). LAMP was generously supported by <a
href="http://icampus.mit.edu">MIT iCampus</a> (MIT/Microsoft Research)
and <a href="http://www.streetfiresound.com">StreetFire Sound
Labs</a>, and was supervised by Professor <a href="http://swiss.csail.mit.edu/users/hal/">Hal Abelson</a>.

